sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant Server

    Note over Client,Server: QUIC runs over UDP port 443
    Note over Client: Generate Connection ID\nGenerate key material

    Client->>Server: Initial packet\n(TLS ClientHello, CRYPTO frame)
    Note over Server: Derive initial secrets\nfrom Connection ID

    Server-->>Client: Initial packet (TLS ServerHello)
    Server-->>Client: Handshake packet\n(EncryptedExtensions, Certificate,\nCertificateVerify, Finished)

    Note over Client: Verify certificate\nDerive handshake keys
    Client->>Server: Handshake packet\n(TLS Finished) [1 RTT complete]

    Note over Client,Server: Application data keys derived
    Client->>Server: 1-RTT packet: HTTP/3 request [encrypted]
    Server-->>Client: 1-RTT packet: HTTP/3 response [encrypted]

    Note over Client,Server: Multiple streams multiplexed\nno head-of-line blocking

    Note over Server: Session ticket for 0-RTT resumption
    Server-->>Client: NEW_TOKEN frame
